- Career trajectory and ambitions (promotions, pivots, industry dynamics)
- Relationship context and support systems that shape major life outcomes
- Health factors or lifestyle patterns that materially affect long-term projections
- Geographic situation and mobility constraints
- Concrete upcoming deadlines, obligations, or life transitions
- Hidden risks or dependencies that could alter the simulation significantly

